# Scene images directory
This directory contains scene background images for the learning environments.

Images should be:
- Format: JPG preferred
- Size: 1200x800 pixels (3:2 aspect ratio)
- Named using scene ID: `{sceneId}.jpg`

Example:
- kitchen.jpg
- living.jpg
- park.jpg
- classroom.jpg
- market.jpg

Use the batch-image-cropper.html tool to standardize images to the correct size and aspect ratio.